snippet.title: A Dark Winter Wander - Trailer
snippet.description:
A short Game boy game about Embla and how she tries to handle the holidays and her strained relationship with her family.

She's drawn into a twilight world of spirits where she undertakes a mysterious year walk, where she might get perspective on things or not.

It's up to you.

Available for free here:
https://redskald.itch.io/a-dark-winter-wander

It's page:
https://redskald.wordpress.com/a-dark-winter-wander/
